1
00:01:30,830 --> 00:01:35,030
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,770 --> 00:01:38,520
[2018]

3
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:37,710
Did you get the movie tickets?

4
00:01:37,710 --> 00:01:38,570
Yeah, got them.

5
00:01:38,789 --> 00:01:40,229
Your favorite—a romance film.

6
00:01:40,229 --> 00:01:40,640
Great.

7
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:42,130
I even got you popcorn.

8
00:01:47,509 --> 00:01:48,590
Sorry, I'm late.

9
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:50,050
Why aren't you going in?

10
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,289
Your friend?

11
00:01:51,789 --> 00:01:52,150
No.

12
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:53,200
Let's go.

13
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:53,560
Okay.

14
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,509
Here. Happy Valentine's Day.

15
00:01:55,509 --> 00:01:56,110
Thank you.

16
00:01:57,039 --> 00:01:58,440
There are always moments

17
00:01:58,509 --> 00:02:00,370
when everyone else is coupled up,

18
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,430
and I'm all alone.

19
00:02:01,310 --> 00:02:04,090
[Episode 23: Where Is My Happiness?]

20
00:02:12,190 --> 00:02:13,120
How is she doing?

21
00:02:13,430 --> 00:02:14,430
Still in surgery.

22
00:02:14,470 --> 00:02:15,870
Wei went to find out more.

23
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,710
Ms. Xia.

24
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:21,690
Don't worry.

25
00:02:22,079 --> 00:02:23,310
We're all here for you.

26
00:02:23,310 --> 00:02:23,840
Zhenzhu.

27
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,100
We're all here.

28
00:02:31,310 --> 00:02:32,190
That man

29
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:33,800
is Li's stepfather.

30
00:02:34,190 --> 00:02:35,910
Li's mother is bedridden due to paralysis.

31
00:02:35,910 --> 00:02:37,870
Her stepfather treats them very badly—

32
00:02:37,870 --> 00:02:39,710
always hitting or scolding them.

33
00:02:39,710 --> 00:02:40,430
So Li

34
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:41,690
has been saving money,

35
00:02:41,710 --> 00:02:43,570
hoping to take her mother away
from Shengcheng.

36
00:02:43,570 --> 00:02:45,000
She's saved up quite a bit already

37
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,520
and plans to leave next month.

38
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,800
That's also

39
00:02:48,150 --> 00:02:48,840
why she said

40
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,970
she couldn't be Xiaolan's assistant.

41
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,240
How badly is that man hurt?

42
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:55,079
Li didn't even touch him!

43
00:02:55,079 --> 00:02:56,079
He fell on his own

44
00:02:56,079 --> 00:02:56,540
and then

45
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,360
landed on... uh...

46
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,560
a broken beer bottle.

47
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,400
If you ask me, he got what he deserved!

48
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,660
Should've been worse!

49
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,410
It's good that it wasn't fatal.

50
00:03:04,190 --> 00:03:05,630
With a man like him,

51
00:03:05,730 --> 00:03:06,280
his family

52
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,240
won't be easy to deal with either.

53
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,080
If he had actually died

54
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,120
and his family came to make trouble,

55
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:11,240
it would only
make things worse for You Li.

56
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:11,870
True.

57
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,200
Are you You Li's friends?

58
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,150
Yes.

59
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,120
We need to speak with her

60
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,780
to understand the situation.

61
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,480
Please take us to her.

62
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,560
Officers,

63
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,190
You Li is my employee.

64
00:03:25,630 --> 00:03:27,870
Her mother, the only family she has
in Shengcheng,

65
00:03:27,870 --> 00:03:29,800
is still lying in the ICU right now,

66
00:03:29,870 --> 00:03:31,630
hovering between life and death.

67
00:03:31,630 --> 00:03:32,829
Chen Gang downstairs

68
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:34,470
said you wanted to kill him.

69
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:35,180
I didn't.

70
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,150
Officers,

71
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:37,760
I'm You Li's lawyer.

72
00:03:38,380 --> 00:03:39,630
I believe you've already confirmed

73
00:03:39,630 --> 00:03:40,490
with the doctor

74
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:42,240
that Chen Gang's injury is in his abdomen,

75
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:43,570
caused by glass shards.

76
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,000
Therefore, his injury

77
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:45,930
has nothing to do

78
00:03:46,079 --> 00:03:46,800
with You Li.

79
00:03:47,790 --> 00:03:48,630
Then, You Li,

80
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,680
how did Chen Gang fall?

81
00:03:55,750 --> 00:03:57,750
He drank too much and fell on his own.

82
00:03:58,600 --> 00:04:00,200
He gets dead drunk every day.

83
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:02,440
When he's drunk, he beats my mom and me!

84
00:04:02,590 --> 00:04:03,870
The neighbors all know.

85
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:05,210
You can go ask them.

86
00:04:06,310 --> 00:04:07,710
When I came back today,

87
00:04:08,470 --> 00:04:11,030
my mom had already been beaten
half to death by him.

88
00:04:11,030 --> 00:04:13,090
Then what made him get violent today?

89
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,000
Because he found out

90
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,529
I wanted to take my mom away.

91
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:19,720
I wanted to get away from him.

92
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,310
If I stayed any longer,

93
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:22,270
he would've beaten

94
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:23,930
both my mother and me to death!

95
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:24,830
Officers,

96
00:04:25,580 --> 00:04:27,160
You Li had a promotion within reach.

97
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,750
She gave it up precisely because she

98
00:04:28,750 --> 00:04:30,480
needed to take her mother away.

99
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:32,190
Who would throw away
such a good opportunity

100
00:04:32,190 --> 00:04:34,650
unless they had
absolutely no other choice?

101
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:36,460
Listen,

102
00:04:37,070 --> 00:04:38,930
your mother needs care right now.

103
00:04:39,150 --> 00:04:41,040
Don't leave Shengcheng for the time being.

104
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,360
We need to be able to find you at any time

105
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:44,020
to understand the situation.

106
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:44,800
What about Chen Gang

107
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,930
beating her mother?

108
00:04:46,310 --> 00:04:47,000
Officers!

109
00:04:48,510 --> 00:04:49,390
I was there too.

110
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,240
If there's anything you need to know,

111
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,040
you can ask me.

112
00:04:51,100 --> 00:04:51,680
That bastard

113
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,120
hit her mother in the head with a stick.

114
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,560
And her mother couldn't even move.

115
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,420
Attorney Zhou,

116
00:04:55,430 --> 00:04:57,560
would that count as attempted murder?

117
00:04:58,270 --> 00:04:59,480
Officers, I believe

118
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,720
you'll make the right judgment.

119
00:05:01,750 --> 00:05:02,480
Don't worry.

120
00:05:03,570 --> 00:05:04,310
We will continue

121
00:05:04,310 --> 00:05:05,870
our investigation into Chen Gang.

122
00:05:05,870 --> 00:05:07,120
Take good care of your mother.

123
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,180
We'll be going now.

124
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:08,840
Let's go.

125
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:09,390
Thank you.

126
00:05:09,390 --> 00:05:09,990
Thank you.

127
00:05:14,940 --> 00:05:15,830
What are you doing?

128
00:05:15,830 --> 00:05:16,230
Get up.

129
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:19,560
Thank you.

130
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:22,270
Thank you all.

131
00:05:24,070 --> 00:05:25,400
Go check on your mother.

132
00:05:33,780 --> 00:05:35,580
The patient is out of danger now,

133
00:05:35,650 --> 00:05:37,630
but I can't say for sure

134
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,250
whether she'll wake up.

135
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:41,800
The patient has been paralyzed for years,

136
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,710
and this time the trauma was severe.

137
00:05:43,710 --> 00:05:44,390
Aside from standard

138
00:05:44,390 --> 00:05:45,520
medical treatment,

139
00:05:45,980 --> 00:05:47,270
your support as family members

140
00:05:47,270 --> 00:05:48,120
and the patient's

141
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,180
own will to survive

142
00:05:49,270 --> 00:05:50,430
are both very important.

143
00:05:50,430 --> 00:05:52,030
Please take good care of her.

144
00:05:52,220 --> 00:05:53,100
It's my job.

145
00:05:53,510 --> 00:05:54,840
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

146
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:03,320
You Li,

147
00:06:04,310 --> 00:06:05,040
don't worry.

148
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:07,160
If there's any update from the police,

149
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,480
they'll contact me first.

150
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:10,040
Just focus on taking care of your mom.

151
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:10,800
If you need anything,

152
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:11,460
just say it.

153
00:06:11,850 --> 00:06:13,000
We have plenty of hands at the shop—

154
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:14,000
we can all help out.

155
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:14,400
Right.

156
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:16,830
Don't hesitate to ask
our Sis Bai for help.

157
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:17,310
Li,

158
00:06:18,310 --> 00:06:19,000
you must want

159
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,260
your mother to wake up,

160
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:20,750
right?

161
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,510
Then you should let her

162
00:06:23,510 --> 00:06:25,630
receive proper treatment here
in the hospital.

163
00:06:25,630 --> 00:06:27,430
Don't worry about the expenses.

164
00:06:27,630 --> 00:06:29,560
The company will cover it upfront.

165
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:30,560
Ms. Xia,

166
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:33,440
I know how costly medical treatment
can be.

167
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,780
This is too much...

168
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,070
I said,

169
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,000
we'll only cover it upfront.

170
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,310
Don't feel burdened by it.

171
00:06:39,310 --> 00:06:41,370
Think of it as a loan from the company.

172
00:06:41,870 --> 00:06:43,000
From now on, I'll deduct

173
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,120
part of your salary each month

174
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,159
as repayment.

175
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,330
Is that okay?

176
00:06:47,159 --> 00:06:47,600
Okay.

177
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,860
Thank you, Ms. Xia.

178
00:06:50,630 --> 00:06:51,830
For the next few days,

179
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,130
stay here

180
00:06:53,159 --> 00:06:54,760
and take care of your mother.

181
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:56,260
When she gets a bit better,

182
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,540
you can come back to work anytime.

183
00:07:00,270 --> 00:07:01,390
Come back to work?

184
00:07:03,070 --> 00:07:03,750
Ms. Xia...

185
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:05,830
you still want me

186
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:07,030
to be your assistant?

187
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:08,760
Of course.

188
00:07:09,390 --> 00:07:10,560
You've always been my top choice

189
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:11,560
for an assistant.

190
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,190
Li,

191
00:07:13,830 --> 00:07:15,160
I really believe in you.

192
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,770
You are smart

193
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:17,920
and capable.

194
00:07:18,270 --> 00:07:18,920
Why shouldn't you

195
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,160
have a better job

196
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,060
and a brighter future?

197
00:07:27,190 --> 00:07:27,800
Ms. Xia...

198
00:07:29,870 --> 00:07:30,480
thank you.

199
00:07:32,470 --> 00:07:33,270
It's nothing.

200
00:07:40,270 --> 00:07:41,730
Shengcheng's city lights

201
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,380
get brighter every night.

202
00:07:43,630 --> 00:07:44,159
Yes.

203
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,460
There used to be nothing here.

204
00:07:46,950 --> 00:07:48,680
Now it's home to so many people.

205
00:07:49,270 --> 00:07:50,600
My mother used to think

206
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:52,920
that only our hometown was home.

207
00:07:53,310 --> 00:07:55,710
She doesn't think that way anymore either.

208
00:07:56,900 --> 00:07:58,960
When you're with the people you love,

209
00:07:59,070 --> 00:08:00,670
anywhere can feel like home.

210
00:08:03,510 --> 00:08:04,310
You know what?

211
00:08:04,830 --> 00:08:06,780
Li today reminded me of

212
00:08:06,810 --> 00:08:08,870
when I first woke up in the Xia family.

213
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:11,790
Only when you've been pushed
to the very edge

214
00:08:11,790 --> 00:08:14,390
do you find the strength
to fight for your life.

215
00:08:17,630 --> 00:08:18,360
Li...

216
00:08:19,430 --> 00:08:20,430
is a brave girl.

217
00:08:21,510 --> 00:08:22,480
She deserves

218
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,190
a better life.

219
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,310
Yeah.

220
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:29,120
But I know how hard

221
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:29,920
that path is.

222
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,340
Zhou Cheng,

223
00:08:32,390 --> 00:08:33,200
tell me,

224
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,530
why do we try our hardest

225
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:36,360
yet still

226
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:38,559
can't find more happiness?

227
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:43,090
Because once you set out on this road,

228
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,920
there's no stopping.

229
00:08:46,510 --> 00:08:48,240
Life was never meant to be easy.

230
00:08:48,910 --> 00:08:49,480
So naturally,

231
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:51,810
there isn't all that much happiness in it.

232
00:08:52,150 --> 00:08:53,280
But because of that,

233
00:08:54,030 --> 00:08:55,240
those fleeting

234
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,440
moments of happiness

235
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:57,940
are all the more precious.

236
00:09:00,630 --> 00:09:01,240
Yeah.

237
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:04,480
I know I shouldn't be so greedy.

238
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,300
But Zhou Cheng,

239
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,200
I still hope

240
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:10,670
there can be more happy moments—

241
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:12,390
for you,

242
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:13,390
me,

243
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:14,800
and everyone.

244
00:09:16,030 --> 00:09:16,630
Oh, right,

245
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:18,600
Du Zhaohui mentioned

246
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:21,120
-that he found Granny Yu's antiques...
-Xiaolan.

247
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,550
You already had a long day.

248
00:09:22,550 --> 00:09:23,680
Let's not talk about

249
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,920
anything else today,

250
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:25,670
okay?

251
00:09:45,510 --> 00:09:46,600
Have you noted down

252
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,490
all the adjustments needed?

253
00:09:47,490 --> 00:09:47,970
Got it.

254
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:48,870
During construction,

255
00:09:48,870 --> 00:09:50,000
safety comes first.

256
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:50,720
-Got it.
-Yes.

257
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,050
Alright, go get to work.

258
00:09:52,390 --> 00:09:52,850
Ms. Xia!

259
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:55,030
We've arranged a place for You Li.

260
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:56,600
It's close to
both the hospital and the company.

261
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,550
I stopped by the hospital earlier

262
00:09:57,550 --> 00:09:58,910
and dropped off the keys.

263
00:09:58,910 --> 00:09:59,910
How is her mother?

264
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,120
She hasn't woken up yet.

265
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:01,750
But her condition

266
00:10:01,750 --> 00:10:03,350
is better than two weeks ago.

267
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:05,630
Li plans to hire a daytime caregiver.

268
00:10:05,630 --> 00:10:07,030
She wants to come back to work.

269
00:10:07,030 --> 00:10:07,440
Okay.

270
00:10:07,670 --> 00:10:09,080
Then help her get familiar

271
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:09,790
with the company's operations first.

272
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:10,150
Okay.

273
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:12,730
Xiaolan,

274
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:13,870
come here.

275
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:14,720
Mr. Mao.

276
00:10:17,750 --> 00:10:20,550
You're always telling others
to stay on top of their work,

277
00:10:20,550 --> 00:10:21,790
but I think you're letting

278
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:22,750
your own slide.

279
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,200
You talk a big game—

280
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,870
learn from my experience

281
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:28,150
and get some hands-on practice.

282
00:10:28,150 --> 00:10:29,200
But what happened?

283
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,320
You just leave the construction site to me

284
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,320
and run off.

285
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:33,770
You're not even as attentive as Du.

286
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,200
Du?

287
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:39,270
Du's been here every day
supervising the site.

288
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:40,390
Xiaolan, listen—

289
00:10:40,980 --> 00:10:42,550
you really need to learn from Du

290
00:10:42,550 --> 00:10:43,310
on this.

291
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,100
Architectural design

292
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:47,670
isn't just about finishing drawings.

293
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:50,010
You need to follow through
with the project's progress.

294
00:10:50,010 --> 00:10:51,400
Only then can you spot

295
00:10:51,550 --> 00:10:52,360
problems

296
00:10:52,390 --> 00:10:53,320
in your designs

297
00:10:53,630 --> 00:10:55,270
and improve them later.

298
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:56,720
Yes.

299
00:10:56,910 --> 00:10:58,170
You're right, Mr. Mao.

300
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:58,960
Mr. Mao,

301
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,240
if the lecture is over,

302
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:01,360
can you let me

303
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:02,910
have Ms. Xia for a moment?

304
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:05,580
Alright, you two talk.

305
00:11:07,550 --> 00:11:08,390
Du, Du?

306
00:11:08,790 --> 00:11:10,250
I've sold my house and car.

307
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,670
Now, I'm just plain Du,
not a young master anymore.

308
00:11:11,670 --> 00:11:14,000
You have to take responsibility for that.

309
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:16,360
I'll be responsible for your investment.

310
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:18,620
The electronics industry is the future.

311
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:21,400
Building an electronics mall
is a sure win.

312
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,670
Yeah, yeah.

313
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:25,240
As for the antiques you asked me to find,

314
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,440
I've put the word out.

315
00:11:26,770 --> 00:11:28,810
A few similar pieces

316
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:30,360
have appeared in antique shops recently.

317
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:32,560
Some details match what you described,

318
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:33,750
but I need more information

319
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:35,410
to compare them more clearly.

320
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:37,200
Is there any way

321
00:11:37,510 --> 00:11:38,570
to get some photos?

322
00:11:38,790 --> 00:11:39,910
The Yu family sold

323
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:41,450
quite a lot of antiques.

324
00:11:41,550 --> 00:11:42,720
Granny Yu can't remember

325
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:44,450
the specific details clearly.

326
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:45,510
But if there were photos,

327
00:11:45,510 --> 00:11:46,960
she'd definitely remember.

328
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:47,320
Okay.

329
00:11:47,510 --> 00:11:48,770
I'll ask around again.

330
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:52,440
If I manage to get the photos,

331
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:53,510
I wonder if you

332
00:11:53,510 --> 00:11:54,710
might do me the honor.

333
00:11:58,960 --> 00:11:59,720
You know

334
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,600
that resort by Qingyue Lake?

335
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:04,200
The one the Americans built?

336
00:12:04,380 --> 00:12:04,690
Yes.

337
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:06,030
I read in the newspaper

338
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,450
that it's opening soon.

339
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:08,390
So,

340
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:10,080
would you do me the honor

341
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:12,520
of attending the resort's opening with me?

342
00:12:14,670 --> 00:12:15,130
I can't.

343
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:16,920
I already have plans.

344
00:12:49,620 --> 00:12:51,000
My leg is broken! My leg is broken!

345
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:51,550
My leg!

346
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:53,290
You have to pay for this!

347
00:12:56,030 --> 00:12:57,760
You did that on purpose, right?

348
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:59,030
Do you know

349
00:12:59,030 --> 00:12:59,910
what that behavior of yours is called?

350
00:12:59,910 --> 00:13:00,840
Staging a crash.

351
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:02,860
Staging a what?

352
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:05,250
Meaning a scam.

353
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,320
Scam?

354
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:06,960
I...

355
00:13:07,870 --> 00:13:08,280
Well,

356
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,510
you made me take a huge fall.

357
00:13:09,510 --> 00:13:10,270
S-Shouldn't you

358
00:13:10,270 --> 00:13:11,150
compensate me somehow?

359
00:13:11,150 --> 00:13:13,010
A-And you said I s-staged a crash?

360
00:13:13,150 --> 00:13:14,280
Did I crash into you?

361
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:16,270
Where did I crash into you? Tell me!

362
00:13:16,270 --> 00:13:16,870
Did I crash into you?

363
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:18,030
When did I ever crash into you?

364
00:13:18,030 --> 00:13:18,390
I...

365
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:19,600
I...

366
00:13:20,870 --> 00:13:21,200
I...

367
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:22,410
What do you want?

368
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:25,030
It's alright. Ignore him.

369
00:13:25,030 --> 00:13:26,270
He's just a sleazy thug.

370
00:13:26,270 --> 00:13:27,320
Hey, who are you calling a sleazy thug?

371
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,200
-You.
-You.

372
00:13:29,390 --> 00:13:30,480
This is not over!

373
00:13:34,910 --> 00:13:36,030
Are you okay, Xiaolan?

374
00:13:36,030 --> 00:13:36,560
I'm fine.

375
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:41,550
It's quite cold.

376
00:13:41,550 --> 00:13:42,390
You want to try that?

377
00:13:42,390 --> 00:13:43,250
Yeah, that one.

378
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,320
That one looks fun too.

379
00:13:47,670 --> 00:13:48,800
Let's go take a look.

380
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,170
How did it go?

381
00:13:58,910 --> 00:14:01,040
Everything is arranged. Don't worry.

382
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:09,370
Yaozong.

383
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:13,000
Why is it just you two?
Where are the others?

384
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,240
They will be here any minute!

385
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:14,550
I...

386
00:14:15,260 --> 00:14:15,840
T-Then, Jie,

387
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,390
you wait here.

388
00:14:16,390 --> 00:14:17,200
When everyone's here, catch up with us!

389
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:17,730
Let's go.

390
00:14:30,350 --> 00:14:31,830
You bitch! You kicked me?

391
00:14:31,910 --> 00:14:33,640
I'll kill you in a minute. Move!

392
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:40,530
Who are you?

393
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:42,370
What do you want?

394
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:43,840
I want her.

395
00:14:44,750 --> 00:14:46,060
Are you trying to bully her?

396
00:14:46,060 --> 00:14:47,660
Hey, mind your own business.

397
00:14:54,390 --> 00:14:55,910
This is a law-governed society,
I'm telling you.

398
00:14:55,910 --> 00:14:56,870
My dad is the village chief.

399
00:14:56,870 --> 00:14:58,030
If you lay a hand on me,
none of you will get away.

400
00:14:58,030 --> 00:14:58,870
Believe it or not, I'll make sure

401
00:14:58,870 --> 00:15:00,130
you never make it back!

402
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,750
Make sure I never make it back?

403
00:15:01,750 --> 00:15:02,120
I...

404
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:12,720
Nobody move!

405
00:15:12,750 --> 00:15:13,790
Surround them!

406
00:15:16,550 --> 00:15:17,950
What are you waiting for?

407
00:15:18,510 --> 00:15:19,870
The loser ends up in the hospital;

408
00:15:19,870 --> 00:15:21,110
the winner ends up in court.

409
00:15:21,110 --> 00:15:23,000
Either way, nobody comes out ahead.

410
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,130
Still want to fight?

411
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:25,680
Yaozong.

412
00:15:26,630 --> 00:15:27,790
Maybe we should just let it go.

413
00:15:27,790 --> 00:15:28,790
It's not worth it.

414
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:29,960
They have knives.

415
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:31,480
Okay.

416
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:35,080
I... I'm in a good mood today.

417
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:37,010
I'll let you off the hook this time.

418
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:39,540
Still trying to act tough?

419
00:15:40,630 --> 00:15:41,690
Get out of here now!

420
00:15:41,790 --> 00:15:43,650
I.. Go, go, go! Hurry up! Let's go!

421
00:15:47,390 --> 00:15:49,320
Alright, everyone, get in the car!

422
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:50,030
Xiaolan,

423
00:15:50,550 --> 00:15:52,150
page me if you need anything!

424
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,390
I'm off now!

425
00:15:53,670 --> 00:15:54,870
Okay, thanks, Uncle!

426
00:15:55,270 --> 00:15:56,330
Drive safe, Uncle!

427
00:15:59,320 --> 00:15:59,780
Sis Bai,

428
00:16:00,200 --> 00:16:00,600
San,

429
00:16:00,750 --> 00:16:01,200
Wei,

430
00:16:01,510 --> 00:16:02,310
thank you all.

431
00:16:02,750 --> 00:16:03,480
No problem.

432
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:04,360
Don't mention it.

433
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:05,360
We're all family.

434
00:16:05,890 --> 00:16:06,200
By the way,

435
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:07,200
when I came over just now,

436
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:07,670
I noticed a place over there—

437
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:08,720
it's huge and looks really fun.

438
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:09,320
Let's take a break

439
00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:10,790
and have some fun together?

440
00:16:10,790 --> 00:16:11,450
We'll pass.

441
00:16:11,560 --> 00:16:12,910
We'll just walk around nearby.

442
00:16:12,910 --> 00:16:13,870
We've got something else to attend to.

443
00:16:13,870 --> 00:16:14,550
You guys have fun.

444
00:16:14,550 --> 00:16:15,720
You've got other business.

445
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:16,600
Come on, here!

446
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:17,440
Cheng,

447
00:16:17,910 --> 00:16:19,170
protect Xiaolan well.

448
00:16:19,750 --> 00:16:20,750
Come on, let's go.

449
00:16:20,840 --> 00:16:21,440
We're off!

450
00:16:21,510 --> 00:16:21,870
Bye!

451
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:22,650
Bye-bye!

452
00:16:22,790 --> 00:16:23,670
It'll definitely be fun.

453
00:16:23,670 --> 00:16:24,630
Where is the place?

454
00:16:24,630 --> 00:16:26,290
What? Is there a Ferris wheel?

455
00:16:33,370 --> 00:16:34,480
The way you play with the knife

456
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:35,880
reminds me of Peter Chan.

457
00:16:36,790 --> 00:16:37,510
Who is he?

458
00:16:39,630 --> 00:16:40,430
From Gangdao.

459
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:42,030
From Gangdao?

460
00:16:42,670 --> 00:16:43,730
Never heard of him.

461
00:16:45,270 --> 00:16:47,000
You'll hear about him someday.

462
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:49,670
Mr. Zhou,

463
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:51,320
you had a reason

464
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:52,140
for bringing me out here, didn't you?

465
00:16:52,140 --> 00:16:54,340
It can't just be a casual stroll, right?

466
00:16:54,630 --> 00:16:55,960
You said it was a day out,

467
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:58,250
but really it's a site visit, isn't it?

468
00:16:58,270 --> 00:16:58,750
Ms. Xia,

469
00:16:59,390 --> 00:17:00,240
the Americans

470
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,360
built a resort here

471
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:02,750
and a golf course.

472
00:17:03,030 --> 00:17:04,440
That clearly means

473
00:17:04,440 --> 00:17:05,480
the project's location is excellent.

474
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:08,740
So wouldn't it also be suitable
for property development?

475
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:10,640
Since you put it that way, Mr. Zhou,

476
00:17:10,640 --> 00:17:12,700
have you already picked a spot for me?

477
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:14,790
When I came out earlier to make a call

478
00:17:14,790 --> 00:17:15,849
and passed by here,

479
00:17:16,030 --> 00:17:17,089
it suddenly hit me.

480
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:18,589
Look.

481
00:18:08,440 --> 00:18:10,270
You're staring at this stinking ditch,

482
00:18:10,270 --> 00:18:11,200
practically drooling over it—

483
00:18:11,200 --> 00:18:13,160
it's really weird.

484
00:18:14,300 --> 00:18:15,550
Didn't you bring me here

485
00:18:15,550 --> 00:18:17,160
just to check this plot of land?

486
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:18,490
Didn't someone once say

487
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:20,940
the three principles of real estate are:

488
00:18:21,110 --> 00:18:24,510
-location, location, location?
-Location, location, location.

489
00:18:24,510 --> 00:18:26,770
This place looks messy and run-down now,

490
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:28,710
but its geographic position

491
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:29,720
is exceptional.

492
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:33,110
This side is the Qingyue Lake Resort,

493
00:18:33,480 --> 00:18:34,680
and on the other side is the golf course

494
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:36,810
that the Americans are about to build.

495
00:18:36,830 --> 00:18:38,420
It sits right between the two—

496
00:18:38,420 --> 00:18:39,400
just like the pearl

497
00:18:39,400 --> 00:18:42,400
in the classic motif
where two dragons chase after it.

498
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:43,510
Mr. Zhou,

499
00:18:43,750 --> 00:18:44,810
you have a good eye.

500
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:47,610
But there's still one problem.

501
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:49,640
This plot sits right
between the two pieces of land

502
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:50,840
the Americans chose.

503
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:51,880
So why was this particular piece

504
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:52,750
left out?

505
00:18:53,240 --> 00:18:54,250
Just because

506
00:18:54,310 --> 00:18:55,570
it's a stinking ditch?

507
00:18:56,370 --> 00:18:57,300
That can't be it.

508
00:18:57,550 --> 00:18:58,920
No developer

509
00:18:58,920 --> 00:19:00,310
would pass up a plot

510
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:01,270
with such a prime location

511
00:19:01,270 --> 00:19:02,920
for something superficial like that.

512
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:04,480
There must be other underlying issues.

513
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:06,610
I'll go back and have them look into it.

514
00:19:08,270 --> 00:19:10,000
I didn't bring my cell phone.

515
00:19:10,310 --> 00:19:12,440
I need to contact Ge Jian immediately.

516
00:19:13,830 --> 00:19:15,750
Ms. Xia, you really
make every second count.

517
00:19:15,750 --> 00:19:16,310
Of course,

518
00:19:16,310 --> 00:19:17,510
time waits for no one!

519
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:20,350
That piece of land

520
00:19:20,550 --> 00:19:22,510
should be about 20 mu.

521
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:25,030
Based on the price the Americans paid,

522
00:19:25,030 --> 00:19:27,400
it's about 150,000 per mu.

523
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:28,640
That means

524
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:30,520
if we can come up with three million,

525
00:19:30,520 --> 00:19:31,980
we should be able to get it.

526
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:34,960
The dividends from

527
00:19:34,980 --> 00:19:36,400
the materials center and Luna

528
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:38,350
for this quarter should be 1.5 million.

529
00:19:38,350 --> 00:19:40,110
Plus the money I've saved up,

530
00:19:40,110 --> 00:19:42,110
and Du Zhaohui's consulting fee...

531
00:19:45,310 --> 00:19:46,790
As for Du Zhaohui,

532
00:19:47,030 --> 00:19:48,920
better not count on anything from him

533
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:50,410
before his Electronics City opens.

534
00:19:50,410 --> 00:19:51,240
Uncle might

535
00:19:51,270 --> 00:19:52,030
still be able to

536
00:19:52,030 --> 00:19:53,430
free up some funds for me.

537
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:55,380
All things considered...

538
00:19:56,590 --> 00:19:57,990
we might be able to get it.

539
00:19:59,410 --> 00:20:02,040
Although the exact price and acreage

540
00:20:02,070 --> 00:20:04,070
will need to be officially assessed
by the government,

541
00:20:04,070 --> 00:20:05,110
it won't vary by more than

542
00:20:05,110 --> 00:20:06,000
100,000.

543
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:08,520
So it really should be feasible.

544
00:20:10,270 --> 00:20:11,800
After saving up for so long,

545
00:20:12,310 --> 00:20:14,510
I finally have enough to get in the game.

546
00:20:15,160 --> 00:20:17,020
So, we have the money for the land.

547
00:20:17,270 --> 00:20:19,470
What about the money for construction?

548
00:20:19,590 --> 00:20:21,000
For construction...

549
00:20:21,550 --> 00:20:23,270
we'll have to take a bit of a risk.

550
00:20:23,270 --> 00:20:25,310
What... kind of risk?

551
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:28,440
We'll take out loans.

552
00:20:28,830 --> 00:20:29,440
Step one:

553
00:20:29,830 --> 00:20:31,200
take out a mortgage loan.

554
00:20:31,200 --> 00:20:32,070
Once we have the land,

555
00:20:32,070 --> 00:20:33,000
we can mortgage it

556
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:34,270
to the bank for a loan.

557
00:20:34,550 --> 00:20:35,400
That money

558
00:20:35,400 --> 00:20:36,550
will serve as

559
00:20:36,550 --> 00:20:37,720
our initial capital

560
00:20:37,750 --> 00:20:39,110
to begin construction.

561
00:20:39,440 --> 00:20:40,000
Step two:

562
00:20:40,240 --> 00:20:41,240
sell off-plan.

563
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:43,270
Reserve your off-plan apartment—
delivery in a year!

564
00:20:43,270 --> 00:20:44,160
Starting now!

565
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:45,510
-I want one!
-I want one!

566
00:20:45,510 --> 00:20:47,200
After the bank loan comes through,

567
00:20:47,200 --> 00:20:49,200
we can build a model building first.

568
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:50,850
With that as a reference,

569
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:52,370
we can start pre-sales.

570
00:20:52,400 --> 00:20:54,460
Which is what people
from Gangdao often do:

571
00:20:54,460 --> 00:20:55,660
sell off-plan apartments.

572
00:20:55,660 --> 00:20:56,880
The deposits from the first buyers

573
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:58,960
can then fund
the construction of the next building.

574
00:20:58,960 --> 00:21:01,120
That does sound feasible.

575
00:21:01,830 --> 00:21:03,080
But every sum of money

576
00:21:03,110 --> 00:21:04,510
has to line up perfectly.

577
00:21:05,030 --> 00:21:06,920
If there's even a slight glitch

578
00:21:07,070 --> 00:21:09,000
or a delay in funds coming through,

579
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:11,600
the entire cash flow
could break at any moment.

580
00:21:11,920 --> 00:21:13,310
It is indeed a bit risky.

581
00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:15,110
But a location this good

582
00:21:15,270 --> 00:21:16,670
is really hard to come by.

583
00:21:16,960 --> 00:21:18,440
If I give up now,

584
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:19,790
I'm afraid

585
00:21:19,790 --> 00:21:21,000
that every time I pass by there,

586
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:21,860
I'll regret it.

587
00:21:22,960 --> 00:21:25,290
Ever since I chose to study architecture,

588
00:21:25,350 --> 00:21:27,280
I've been waiting for this moment.

589
00:21:27,480 --> 00:21:28,880
So I don't want to give up.

590
00:21:29,350 --> 00:21:30,550
I want to give it a try.

591
00:21:31,440 --> 00:21:31,770
Okay.

592
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:34,180
Since you've decided,

593
00:21:34,750 --> 00:21:36,080
I'm with you all the way.

594
00:21:38,110 --> 00:21:39,170
More importantly,

595
00:21:39,480 --> 00:21:40,540
I really don't know

596
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:42,680
how much time I have left.

597
00:21:45,760 --> 00:21:46,560
But, Xiaolan,

598
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:48,640
most housing nowadays

599
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:50,750
is still allocated by work units.

600
00:21:51,510 --> 00:21:52,200
Very few people

601
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:53,680
actually buy commercial housing,

602
00:21:53,680 --> 00:21:54,640
let alone

603
00:21:54,720 --> 00:21:55,960
buy something they can't even see yet—

604
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:57,290
just a promise on paper.

605
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:59,110
I feel like this is

606
00:21:59,510 --> 00:22:00,200
just like

607
00:22:00,200 --> 00:22:01,260
that resort hotel—

608
00:22:01,270 --> 00:22:02,310
only a very small number of people

609
00:22:02,310 --> 00:22:03,110
can afford it.

610
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:04,200
So,

611
00:22:04,550 --> 00:22:05,920
our target customers are

612
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:07,680
the Gangdao businesspeople
who have come to

613
00:22:07,680 --> 00:22:09,510
Shengcheng for business
and are already familiar

614
00:22:09,510 --> 00:22:11,570
with the off-plan property concept.

615
00:22:12,830 --> 00:22:14,760
The hard part isn't buying the land

616
00:22:14,830 --> 00:22:16,000
but getting the apartments sold.

617
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:18,330
People from Gangdao care a lot about luck.

618
00:22:18,480 --> 00:22:19,070
The news

619
00:22:19,070 --> 00:22:21,070
that the Americans passed on this plot

620
00:22:21,070 --> 00:22:22,670
will get out sooner or later.

621
00:22:23,040 --> 00:22:25,320
We need a good story

622
00:22:25,350 --> 00:22:26,920
to reshape how buyers

623
00:22:27,270 --> 00:22:28,880
see the smelly ditch.

624
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:31,730
I can figure all that out later.

625
00:22:32,070 --> 00:22:32,850
Right now, I need to think about

626
00:22:32,850 --> 00:22:34,450
what other steps are needed.

627
00:22:39,720 --> 00:22:41,240
Is it about the hospital?

628
00:22:42,510 --> 00:22:43,640
It's okay. Go ahead.

629
00:22:45,720 --> 00:22:46,160
Okay.

630
00:22:47,830 --> 00:22:48,360
Bye-bye.

631
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:03,500
After dreaming about this for so long...

632
00:23:04,550 --> 00:23:06,150
can I finally make it happen?

633
00:23:07,510 --> 00:23:08,120
Ms. Xia,

634
00:23:08,480 --> 00:23:09,750
it's not impossible for you

635
00:23:09,750 --> 00:23:10,750
to purchase land.

636
00:23:11,160 --> 00:23:11,830
There's already a precedent—

637
00:23:11,830 --> 00:23:13,000
as recently as last year,

638
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:14,350
a private company acquired land.

639
00:23:14,350 --> 00:23:15,270
That's wonderful.

640
00:23:15,270 --> 00:23:16,680
What paperwork do I need?

641
00:23:17,110 --> 00:23:17,640
First,

642
00:23:17,880 --> 00:23:19,030
you need to register

643
00:23:19,350 --> 00:23:20,610
a real estate company.

644
00:23:21,160 --> 00:23:22,290
Qihang Real Estate.

645
00:23:22,510 --> 00:23:23,350
Qihang, as in

646
00:23:23,740 --> 00:23:24,160
setting sail and traveling far.

647
00:23:23,860 --> 00:23:26,020
[Business License;
Legal Representative: Xia Xiaolan]

648
00:23:24,160 --> 00:23:24,590
Then,

649
00:23:24,800 --> 00:23:25,960
you'll also need to affiliate with

650
00:23:25,960 --> 00:23:27,790
a state-owned enterprise
with construction qualifications.

651
00:23:27,790 --> 00:23:28,240
This

652
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:29,750
is the most important step.

653
00:23:29,750 --> 00:23:31,720
Longcheng No. 2 Construction Group?

654
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:32,830
That would be perfect.

655
00:23:32,830 --> 00:23:35,030
I have a former student working there.

656
00:23:35,110 --> 00:23:36,070
I'll reach out to him first for you.

657
00:23:36,070 --> 00:23:36,440
Okay.

658
00:23:36,720 --> 00:23:37,780
Thank you, Mr. Mao.

659
00:23:38,550 --> 00:23:39,080
Finally,

660
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:40,480
you need to prepare

661
00:23:40,510 --> 00:23:42,070
a letter of intent for land lease,

662
00:23:42,070 --> 00:23:43,270
detailing the proposed planning

663
00:23:43,270 --> 00:23:44,200
and purpose of the land.

664
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:45,160
Any content relating to waste management

665
00:23:45,160 --> 00:23:46,480
and improving the city's appearance

666
00:23:46,480 --> 00:23:47,160
can be emphasized

667
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:48,220
and expanded upon.

668
00:23:49,430 --> 00:23:50,000
[Letter of Intent to Lease Land]

669
00:23:49,640 --> 00:23:50,100
Ms. Xia,

670
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:52,360
I went to inquire about it
a couple of days ago.

671
00:23:52,360 --> 00:23:53,480
The subdistrict office sent people

672
00:23:53,480 --> 00:23:54,740
to remeasure the plot.

673
00:23:54,750 --> 00:23:55,610
It's over 20 mu.

674
00:23:55,790 --> 00:23:57,640
Turns out the chief of Ganquan Village

675
00:23:57,640 --> 00:23:58,880
had tampered with the records

676
00:23:58,880 --> 00:23:59,750
during the government's

677
00:23:59,750 --> 00:24:00,810
land acquisition.

678
00:24:01,200 --> 00:24:02,800
It wasn't that the Americans

679
00:24:02,960 --> 00:24:04,000
didn't want this plot;

680
00:24:04,000 --> 00:24:05,860
they just didn't know it existed.

681
00:24:10,070 --> 00:24:11,400
Is he genuinely ignorant of the law,

682
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:13,200
or is he up to something crooked?

683
00:24:13,640 --> 00:24:14,730
Look into it further.

684
00:24:14,730 --> 00:24:15,790
Even though we can just

685
00:24:15,790 --> 00:24:17,160
apply to the government
to acquire the land

686
00:24:17,160 --> 00:24:18,440
and follow the procedure,

687
00:24:18,440 --> 00:24:19,440
I don't want there to be

688
00:24:19,440 --> 00:24:20,720
any hidden trouble later on.

689
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:21,920
Understood, Ms. Xia.

690
00:24:27,770 --> 00:24:29,450
Who parked this car on my road?

691
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:31,000
Sorry, it's ours.

692
00:24:31,030 --> 00:24:31,920
We'll leave in a bit.

693
00:24:31,920 --> 00:24:32,870
Leave now!

694
00:24:33,750 --> 00:24:34,880
Drive it away now!

695
00:24:35,400 --> 00:24:36,140
Drive...

696
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:38,400
Ouch, ouch, ouch!

697
00:24:39,480 --> 00:24:40,830
Hey, you... Don't go!

698
00:24:41,560 --> 00:24:42,680
I'm telling you, this is not over.

699
00:24:42,680 --> 00:24:43,610
You just said...

700
00:24:44,110 --> 00:24:45,110
this is your road?

701
00:24:46,750 --> 00:24:47,120
I...

702
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:48,160
Stop right there!

703
00:24:49,030 --> 00:24:50,090
Last time, you said

704
00:24:50,290 --> 00:24:52,350
your dad is the village chief, right?

705
00:24:52,590 --> 00:24:55,090
I was just taking a shortcut home.

706
00:24:55,870 --> 00:24:57,350
That woman with the knife
isn't around, right?

707
00:24:57,350 --> 00:24:58,150
That woman...

708
00:24:58,200 --> 00:25:00,030
I've turned over a new leaf now.

709
00:25:00,070 --> 00:25:00,790
I haven't set foot

710
00:25:00,790 --> 00:25:01,830
near Qingyue Lake in ages!

711
00:25:01,830 --> 00:25:02,630
Stop yelling.

712
00:25:02,920 --> 00:25:04,120
Answer my questions.

713
00:25:06,830 --> 00:25:08,760
It's the chief! My dad is the chief!

714
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:10,410
Alright.

715
00:25:11,200 --> 00:25:12,730
I won't beat you today then.

716
00:25:13,000 --> 00:25:14,240
Go back and ask your dad

717
00:25:14,240 --> 00:25:15,790
why he concealed
and didn't report this plot

718
00:25:15,790 --> 00:25:17,450
during the land acquisition.

719
00:25:17,680 --> 00:25:18,350
Get a clear answer,

720
00:25:18,350 --> 00:25:20,270
then wait for me here tomorrow morning.

721
00:25:20,270 --> 00:25:21,750
Don't get any funny ideas.

722
00:25:22,350 --> 00:25:24,030
Or else that woman with the knife

723
00:25:24,030 --> 00:25:25,350
might show up anytime.

724
00:25:25,720 --> 00:25:26,450
Okay, ma'am.

725
00:25:27,590 --> 00:25:28,120
Goodbye.

726
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:32,960
Ms. Xia,

727
00:25:33,550 --> 00:25:36,010
can a guy like that
actually get things done?

728
00:25:36,210 --> 00:25:37,160
It doesn't matter.

729
00:25:37,160 --> 00:25:38,730
I wasn't really counting on him anyway.

730
00:25:38,730 --> 00:25:40,270
I just wanted to see if he could spare us

731
00:25:40,270 --> 00:25:41,590
some trouble down the road.

732
00:25:41,590 --> 00:25:42,350
If he fails,

733
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:43,740
it won't affect us.

734
00:26:03,110 --> 00:26:03,590
Ms. Xia,

735
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:05,250
should I go check on him?

736
00:26:05,960 --> 00:26:06,480
No need.

737
00:26:07,430 --> 00:26:10,030
There must be something fishy
about this plot.

738
00:26:18,750 --> 00:26:19,280
Grandpa!

739
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:21,790
Well, Grandpa, open the door!

740
00:26:21,790 --> 00:26:22,320
Grandpa!

741
00:26:23,350 --> 00:26:24,750
What "gold-bearing sand
springing from the ground"?

742
00:26:24,750 --> 00:26:26,640
You were just drunk and seeing things!

743
00:26:26,640 --> 00:26:29,490
Cut the threads of fate...

744
00:26:30,270 --> 00:26:32,100
They said there's gold-bearing sand
in our village.

745
00:26:32,100 --> 00:26:34,240
There can't be any gold-bearing sand here.

746
00:26:34,240 --> 00:26:34,700
Tell me—

747
00:26:34,800 --> 00:26:35,480
isn't it great if we just sell it

748
00:26:35,480 --> 00:26:38,810
and get several hundred thousand
in compensation instead?

749
00:26:39,510 --> 00:26:40,110
If you have the guts,

750
00:26:40,110 --> 00:26:41,310
keep me locked up forever!

751
00:26:41,310 --> 00:26:42,460
Or the day I become the Village Chief,

752
00:26:42,460 --> 00:26:43,160
the first thing I'll do

753
00:26:43,160 --> 00:26:44,760
is sell Stinky Bamboo Ditch!

754
00:26:45,160 --> 00:26:47,490
They can get hundreds of thousands for it!

755
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:50,620
Ms. Xia!

756
00:26:51,800 --> 00:26:53,110
Turns out that brat, Luo Yaozong,

757
00:26:53,110 --> 00:26:54,580
has been locked up by his grandfather.

758
00:26:54,580 --> 00:26:55,370
His grandfather also claims

759
00:26:55,370 --> 00:26:55,960
that this piece of land

760
00:26:55,960 --> 00:26:57,480
is their family's feng shui treasure site,

761
00:26:57,480 --> 00:26:58,480
called something like

762
00:26:58,480 --> 00:26:59,750
"gold-bearing sand
springing from the ground."

763
00:26:59,750 --> 00:27:00,680
Luo Yaozong was in the house

764
00:27:00,680 --> 00:27:01,350
screaming and shouting,

765
00:27:01,350 --> 00:27:02,400
and all the neighbors heard him.

766
00:27:02,400 --> 00:27:03,440
So this matter

767
00:27:03,440 --> 00:27:04,770
wasn't hard to find out.

768
00:27:06,550 --> 00:27:07,200
If that's

769
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:08,160
the reason,

770
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:09,070
it won't affect

771
00:27:09,070 --> 00:27:10,530
our development project.

772
00:27:10,960 --> 00:27:12,440
But will they cause trouble?

773
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:13,920
Should I make a trip to Ganquan Village?

774
00:27:13,920 --> 00:27:14,380
No need.

775
00:27:14,720 --> 00:27:16,200
Better not to stir things up.

776
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:17,310
Before the land deal is signed,

777
00:27:17,310 --> 00:27:18,030
none of us should go

778
00:27:18,030 --> 00:27:18,680
to that place again.

779
00:27:18,680 --> 00:27:19,010
Okay.

780
00:27:23,920 --> 00:27:25,850
The hard part isn't buying the land

781
00:27:26,160 --> 00:27:27,790
but getting the apartments sold.

782
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:29,480
We need a good story.

783
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:32,510
A treasure  site.

784
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:36,320
Gold-bearing sand
springing from the ground.

785
00:27:37,270 --> 00:27:38,790
Hasn't the Luo family just handed me

786
00:27:38,790 --> 00:27:40,240
a ready-made story?

787
00:27:40,720 --> 00:27:42,200
Golden Sands Pool.

788
00:27:44,830 --> 00:27:45,160
Okay.

789
00:27:45,510 --> 00:27:47,440
No problem.
I'll go make the arrangements first.

790
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:47,920
You Li,

791
00:27:48,480 --> 00:27:49,940
how's your mother lately?

792
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:52,440
Same as before.

793
00:27:53,060 --> 00:27:54,920
The doctor said we need to be patient.

794
00:27:54,920 --> 00:27:56,920
I talk to her every day when I get back.

795
00:27:56,920 --> 00:27:57,800
I believe

796
00:27:57,830 --> 00:27:58,690
she can hear me.

797
00:27:59,240 --> 00:28:00,240
I believe so, too.

798
00:28:00,280 --> 00:28:01,240
If you need anything,

799
00:28:01,240 --> 00:28:02,700
just let the company know.

800
00:28:02,960 --> 00:28:03,880
Thank you, Ms. Xia.

801
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:04,880
I'll head out now.

802
00:28:05,110 --> 00:28:05,510
Sure.

803
00:28:10,280 --> 00:28:11,240
Hello.

804
00:28:11,270 --> 00:28:12,400
Qihang Real Estate.

805
00:28:13,120 --> 00:28:14,240
Your land acquisition application

806
00:28:14,240 --> 00:28:15,300
has been approved.

807
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:17,880
Please come by to sign the contract
when you have time.

808
00:28:17,880 --> 00:28:18,880
Great, thank you.

809
00:28:18,960 --> 00:28:20,420
We're available anytime.

810
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:21,850
I've reviewed the contract.

811
00:28:21,850 --> 00:28:24,600
[Letter of Intent to Lease Land]

812
00:28:22,480 --> 00:28:24,070
It's a standard government template,

813
00:28:24,070 --> 00:28:25,920
with not much flexibility for adjustments.

814
00:28:25,920 --> 00:28:27,680
And the wording is quite strong,

815
00:28:27,680 --> 00:28:28,790
but the framework is solid.

816
00:28:28,790 --> 00:28:30,650
So there shouldn't be any issues.

817
00:28:31,070 --> 00:28:32,350
Ms. Xia, you really take contracts

818
00:28:32,350 --> 00:28:33,310
seriously.

819
00:28:34,440 --> 00:28:36,520
Yes, I have to take it seriously.

820
00:28:36,790 --> 00:28:38,160
Look at the contract you signed!

821
00:28:38,160 --> 00:28:39,160
Look at how the joint liability clauses

822
00:28:39,160 --> 00:28:39,640
are written!

823
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:40,830
All our company's losses

824
00:28:40,830 --> 00:28:42,290
will be borne by you alone!

825
00:28:42,960 --> 00:28:43,460
Yeah.

826
00:28:44,270 --> 00:28:45,440
When it comes to contracts,

827
00:28:45,440 --> 00:28:47,040
you can never be too careful.

828
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:48,720
Do you know what's most important

829
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:50,120
when signing a contract?

830
00:28:52,510 --> 00:28:53,730
The most important thing

831
00:28:53,730 --> 00:28:54,890
is to first verify

832
00:28:54,920 --> 00:28:56,270
if the party you're signing with

833
00:28:56,270 --> 00:28:57,000
is reliable.

834
00:28:57,350 --> 00:28:58,210
Only after that

835
00:28:58,310 --> 00:29:00,680
do you verify
the specific terms and clauses.

836
00:29:00,680 --> 00:29:01,270
The party signing with us this time

837
00:29:01,270 --> 00:29:02,440
is the government—

838
00:29:02,510 --> 00:29:04,110
they won't play word games

839
00:29:04,310 --> 00:29:05,040
or lay traps.

840
00:29:05,240 --> 00:29:06,200
So rest assured.

841
00:29:07,680 --> 00:29:08,480
You're right.

842
00:29:08,880 --> 00:29:11,680
The most important thing is
a reliable other party.

843
00:29:11,680 --> 00:29:13,410
If I had understood this sooner

844
00:29:14,070 --> 00:29:15,270
instead of rushing to

845
00:29:15,350 --> 00:29:17,680
get performance bonuses and a promotion,

846
00:29:17,750 --> 00:29:19,750
maybe I wouldn't have ended up here.

847
00:29:19,830 --> 00:29:20,720
Now,

848
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:22,610
I don't know
if that's a good thing or not.

849
00:29:22,610 --> 00:29:24,120
[Meeting Room]

850
00:29:23,590 --> 00:29:24,350
This

851
00:29:24,350 --> 00:29:25,660
is the land lease agreement

852
00:29:25,660 --> 00:29:26,920
we discussed earlier.

853
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:28,160
Take a look.

854
00:29:28,510 --> 00:29:29,560
If everything is in order,

855
00:29:29,560 --> 00:29:30,790
you can sign it.

856
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:32,110
Okay.

857
00:29:35,110 --> 00:29:37,200
Yuanhui took on all the previous projects,

858
00:29:37,200 --> 00:29:39,000
and Uncle signed the contracts.

859
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:40,720
This will be the first time

860
00:29:41,160 --> 00:29:42,880
a contract bears Xia Xiaolan's name—

861
00:29:42,880 --> 00:29:44,640
not as a sales representative,

862
00:29:45,070 --> 00:29:45,830
nor as

863
00:29:46,110 --> 00:29:47,750
a project manager,

864
00:29:47,960 --> 00:29:49,200
but entirely as

865
00:29:49,450 --> 00:29:50,690
the sole director

866
00:29:50,720 --> 00:29:52,110
of Qihang Real Estate.

867
00:29:56,400 --> 00:29:56,880
I know

868
00:29:58,350 --> 00:29:59,240
you'll have

869
00:29:59,550 --> 00:30:00,880
an extraordinary life,

870
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:02,860
and your future

871
00:30:03,240 --> 00:30:04,270
will hold

872
00:30:04,270 --> 00:30:06,270
moments even more brilliant than this one.

873
00:30:06,270 --> 00:30:07,530
Let this accompany you

874
00:30:08,550 --> 00:30:10,750
as you write your brilliant life story.

875
00:30:20,580 --> 00:30:22,680
[Qihang Real Estate Co., Ltd.]

876
00:30:25,480 --> 00:30:26,640
Looks like that letter of intent

877
00:30:26,640 --> 00:30:27,840
was useful after all.

878
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:28,880
The final price came to

879
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:29,920
130,000 yuan per mu,

880
00:30:29,920 --> 00:30:31,240
which is lower than I expected.

881
00:30:31,240 --> 00:30:32,240
But the total area

882
00:30:32,240 --> 00:30:33,640
is 23.5 mu.

883
00:30:33,830 --> 00:30:34,590
So the total comes to

884
00:30:34,590 --> 00:30:35,650
3.05 million yuan—

885
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:37,210
about what we anticipated.

886
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:39,530
To think that back then,

887
00:30:39,680 --> 00:30:40,480
scraping together

888
00:30:40,480 --> 00:30:42,270
1 million yuan
for Luna's advertising fees

889
00:30:42,270 --> 00:30:43,240
felt nearly impossible.

890
00:30:43,240 --> 00:30:45,200
Now, Xiaolan is acquiring land
for 3 million,

891
00:30:45,200 --> 00:30:46,060
just like that.

892
00:30:46,510 --> 00:30:48,110
You know what feeling I have?

893
00:30:48,110 --> 00:30:50,550
Big money, big swagger.

894
00:30:50,880 --> 00:30:51,680
That doesn't sound like

895
00:30:51,680 --> 00:30:53,480
a compliment, the way you put it.

896
00:30:55,750 --> 00:30:56,240
Xia,

897
00:30:57,480 --> 00:30:59,240
everyone helped out with Luna before.

898
00:30:59,240 --> 00:31:01,240
This time, I contributed the least.

899
00:31:01,750 --> 00:31:02,790
It's mainly because

900
00:31:02,790 --> 00:31:04,590
I just bought a production line,

901
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:07,030
so there really isn't
that much cash on hand.

902
00:31:07,030 --> 00:31:07,720
On top of that,

903
00:31:07,720 --> 00:31:08,440
Elegance has been chasing after us,

904
00:31:08,440 --> 00:31:10,480
setting up branches one after another.

905
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:11,340
I had no choice.

906
00:31:11,550 --> 00:31:12,310
So most of the profits

907
00:31:12,310 --> 00:31:13,570
have been reinvested.

908
00:31:13,640 --> 00:31:14,310
Do we know

909
00:31:14,310 --> 00:31:15,590
who's behind Elegance now?

910
00:31:15,590 --> 00:31:16,120
Any idea?

911
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:18,480
I heard it's a Gangdao merchant.

912
00:31:19,270 --> 00:31:21,070
Ji Ya has definitely backed off.

913
00:31:21,240 --> 00:31:22,750
Well, whoever it is,

914
00:31:23,200 --> 00:31:25,030
they're a competitor either way.

915
00:31:25,030 --> 00:31:25,750
Mainly,

916
00:31:25,830 --> 00:31:27,510
I feel a little guilty that I couldn't

917
00:31:27,510 --> 00:31:29,040
help Qihang more this time.

918
00:31:29,350 --> 00:31:30,110
Chen,

919
00:31:30,310 --> 00:31:31,550
don't think like that.

920
00:31:31,550 --> 00:31:32,270
Consider this

921
00:31:32,270 --> 00:31:33,880
as me personally

922
00:31:33,880 --> 00:31:35,110
borrowing money from you.

923
00:31:35,110 --> 00:31:35,880
Besides,

924
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:37,350
I know you've had your eye on

925
00:31:37,350 --> 00:31:38,920
that production line
for Luna for a while now.

926
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:39,790
I can't let my affairs

927
00:31:39,790 --> 00:31:41,190
hold your business back.

928
00:31:41,480 --> 00:31:42,720
On the contrary, doesn't Qihang's

929
00:31:42,720 --> 00:31:43,880
land purchase seem

930
00:31:44,070 --> 00:31:45,200
particularly rash?

931
00:31:46,110 --> 00:31:47,310
Y-You want the truth?

932
00:31:49,720 --> 00:31:51,350
Building houses on a stinking ditch...

933
00:31:51,350 --> 00:31:52,790
Well, I... I think...

934
00:31:53,350 --> 00:31:54,610
What's there to think?

935
00:31:54,720 --> 00:31:55,510
Just trust

936
00:31:55,510 --> 00:31:56,790
Xiaolan, and that's all there is to it.

937
00:31:56,790 --> 00:31:58,310
The building she puts up

938
00:31:58,310 --> 00:31:59,440
will definitely be the best

939
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:00,300
in Shengcheng.

940
00:32:00,920 --> 00:32:01,240
Yeah.

941
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:03,070
Xiaolan must've thought it all through!

942
00:32:03,070 --> 00:32:04,070
Right, right, right.

943
00:32:04,070 --> 00:32:04,760
Anyway,

944
00:32:04,790 --> 00:32:06,720
I'm still very grateful to you all!

945
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:08,680
-Come on, cheers!
-Cheers!

946
00:32:12,210 --> 00:32:13,480
Once the payment is made tomorrow,

947
00:32:13,480 --> 00:32:15,540
all the procedures will be complete.

948
00:32:15,570 --> 00:32:16,370
Next,

949
00:32:16,400 --> 00:32:18,130
it's clearing the site,

950
00:32:18,160 --> 00:32:20,880
surveying, securing loans,
and leveling the foundation.

951
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:22,280
With so much ahead of you,

952
00:32:22,340 --> 00:32:24,200
I think you'll need an assistant.

953
00:32:24,790 --> 00:32:25,400
Yeah.

954
00:32:25,920 --> 00:32:27,920
I'm thinking of giving Ge Jian a try.

955
00:32:28,320 --> 00:32:29,320
What do you think?

956
00:32:31,110 --> 00:32:32,400
Work at the construction site

957
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:34,590
mainly involves dealing with workers.

958
00:32:34,590 --> 00:32:36,520
Ge Jian has martial arts training,

959
00:32:36,720 --> 00:32:38,350
so he commands some authority
over the workers.

960
00:32:38,350 --> 00:32:39,160
And after all these years

961
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:40,000
by your side,

962
00:32:40,270 --> 00:32:41,110
he's picked up a thing or two

963
00:32:41,110 --> 00:32:42,510
about business from you.

964
00:32:42,610 --> 00:32:44,070
He's actually a good choice.

965
00:32:44,070 --> 00:32:44,480
Okay.

966
00:32:44,920 --> 00:32:46,720
Let's give Ge Jian a chance

967
00:32:46,750 --> 00:32:48,350
and see if he's up to the task.

968
00:32:50,350 --> 00:32:52,510
There are still countless things

969
00:32:52,790 --> 00:32:54,400
waiting for me to handle, one by one.

970
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:56,070
I really wish
the Golden Sands Pool project

971
00:32:56,070 --> 00:32:57,730
could be finished overnight.

972
00:32:58,830 --> 00:33:00,350
It seems our Ms. Xia's work

973
00:33:00,480 --> 00:33:02,640
is never-ending.

974
00:33:02,960 --> 00:33:04,000
Attorney Zhou,

975
00:33:04,200 --> 00:33:05,550
are you complaining

976
00:33:05,830 --> 00:33:07,260
or just wanting more attention?

977
00:33:07,260 --> 00:33:08,150
Neither.

978
00:33:08,960 --> 00:33:09,960
I just feel like

979
00:33:10,920 --> 00:33:13,050
you've been unusually rushed lately,

980
00:33:13,440 --> 00:33:14,550
like you want to

981
00:33:14,750 --> 00:33:16,270
get everything done
as quickly as possible.

982
00:33:16,270 --> 00:33:17,480
You've always had determination

983
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:18,280
and boldness,

984
00:33:18,600 --> 00:33:20,460
but you didn't like taking risks.

985
00:33:24,070 --> 00:33:24,680
However,

986
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:26,750
that piece of land is indeed

987
00:33:26,750 --> 00:33:27,590
a rare find.

988
00:33:27,920 --> 00:33:29,450
It would be a pity to miss it.

989
00:33:29,510 --> 00:33:30,000
Ms. Xia,

990
00:33:30,720 --> 00:33:32,150
Qihang's first project

991
00:33:32,640 --> 00:33:34,300
will definitely go smoothly.

992
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:35,130
You can do it.

993
00:33:56,790 --> 00:33:57,920
Wednesday,

994
00:33:58,590 --> 00:34:00,350
October 9th, 1991.

995
00:34:02,510 --> 00:34:03,570
Qihang Real Estate

996
00:34:03,880 --> 00:34:05,810
purchased its first piece of land.

997
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:09,060
I hope the project goes smoothly.

998
00:34:09,550 --> 00:34:11,630
I hope there's still time.

999
00:34:26,590 --> 00:34:27,110
Cheng.

1000
00:34:28,320 --> 00:34:29,580
Look how happy Xiaolan

1001
00:34:29,880 --> 00:34:30,710
was today.

1002
00:34:31,230 --> 00:34:32,070
Think back to when

1003
00:34:32,070 --> 00:34:33,280
we first met her—

1004
00:34:33,670 --> 00:34:35,330
she was still selling duck eggs then.

1005
00:34:35,330 --> 00:34:36,000
She wouldn't even

1006
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:37,030
treat herself to a bowl of noodles.

1007
00:34:37,030 --> 00:34:37,889
Look at her now—

1008
00:34:37,960 --> 00:34:39,360
a real estate developer!

1009
00:34:41,190 --> 00:34:41,630
Yeah.

1010
00:34:42,760 --> 00:34:44,219
I'm very happy for her too.

1011
00:34:45,440 --> 00:34:46,699
I'm just a bit worried—

1012
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:48,900
isn't she being too hasty?

1013
00:34:49,510 --> 00:34:51,280
Xiaolan has always been like this.

1014
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:52,550
She seizes the opportunity
the moment she sees one.

1015
00:34:52,550 --> 00:34:53,469
She's not afraid of failure.

1016
00:34:53,469 --> 00:34:55,190
Failure is no big deal, anyway.

1017
00:34:55,190 --> 00:34:56,670
Never look down on the young

1018
00:34:56,670 --> 00:34:58,960
just because they're poor
or because they're inexperienced, right?

1019
00:34:58,960 --> 00:34:59,710
Besides,

1020
00:34:59,960 --> 00:35:01,960
Xiaolan seems to have never failed.

1021
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:03,360
Right.

1022
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:04,510
And even if she did fail,

1023
00:35:04,510 --> 00:35:05,960
it wouldn't be the end of the world.

1024
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:06,710
It's not like we're

1025
00:35:06,710 --> 00:35:08,510
starting from nothing anymore.

1026
00:35:08,670 --> 00:35:10,030
Exactly.

1027
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:10,850
Alright.

1028
00:35:11,190 --> 00:35:12,650
I'm going to take a shower.

1029
00:35:14,710 --> 00:35:15,440
One day,

1030
00:35:15,440 --> 00:35:16,900
when Xiaolan makes it big,

1031
00:35:17,230 --> 00:35:18,890
she can build a building here,

1032
00:35:19,230 --> 00:35:20,960
and another one there!

1033
00:35:21,320 --> 00:35:22,520
They will all be ours!

1034
00:35:25,030 --> 00:35:25,560
Awesome!

1035
00:35:43,150 --> 00:35:43,550
Hello?

1036
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:45,030
Xiaolan, bad news.

1037
00:35:45,510 --> 00:35:46,550
The Chief of Ganquan Village

1038
00:35:46,550 --> 00:35:48,000
is causing a scene at Stinky Bamboo Ditch!

1039
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:50,110
This is our Luo family's
feng shui treasure site!

1040
00:35:50,110 --> 00:35:51,800
I've guarded it my whole life!

1041
00:35:52,280 --> 00:35:53,630
I'm practically one foot in the grave!

1042
00:35:53,630 --> 00:35:55,510
And you've swindled it away from me!

1043
00:35:55,510 --> 00:35:56,880
You heartless developers!

1044
00:35:56,880 --> 00:35:57,960
You are just evil!

1045
00:35:57,960 --> 00:35:58,620
Heartless!

1046
00:35:58,710 --> 00:35:59,320
You're all heartless!

1047
00:35:59,320 --> 00:36:00,230
Mr. Luo!

1048
00:36:00,230 --> 00:36:00,630
Swindlers!

1049
00:36:00,630 --> 00:36:02,440
We purchased this land legally,

1050
00:36:02,510 --> 00:36:03,930
and we have the right to construct here.

1051
00:36:03,930 --> 00:36:05,440
The notice is already posted!

1052
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:06,030
Nonsense!

1053
00:36:06,030 --> 00:36:06,980
Excuse me! Make way!

1054
00:36:06,980 --> 00:36:08,440
It's a government notice!

1055
00:36:08,670 --> 00:36:09,370
Director Wang,

1056
00:36:09,370 --> 00:36:10,550
what brings you here?

1057
00:36:10,550 --> 00:36:12,190
This is my family's
feng shui treasure site!

1058
00:36:12,190 --> 00:36:13,390
How could you sell it?

1059
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:14,000
Sir,

1060
00:36:14,320 --> 00:36:15,320
please calm down!

1061
00:36:15,920 --> 00:36:17,000
Let's get this straight.

1062
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:17,630
This land

1063
00:36:17,880 --> 00:36:19,070
belongs to the state,

1064
00:36:19,070 --> 00:36:20,550
not your family!

1065
00:36:21,150 --> 00:36:22,800
The city is focused on

1066
00:36:22,960 --> 00:36:24,690
production and construction!

1067
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:25,440
They went through

1068
00:36:25,440 --> 00:36:27,100
the proper approval process!

1069
00:36:28,440 --> 00:36:29,040
Come here.

1070
00:36:32,230 --> 00:36:33,150
Mr. Luo,

1071
00:36:33,400 --> 00:36:34,860
we didn't shortchange you

1072
00:36:34,960 --> 00:36:35,630
a single cent

1073
00:36:35,630 --> 00:36:37,090
on the land compensation.

1074
00:36:37,190 --> 00:36:38,590
Don't get greedy now.

1075
00:36:39,600 --> 00:36:41,190
Now, come on, ask them to leave.

1076
00:36:41,190 --> 00:36:42,030
Okay, okay.

1077
00:36:43,670 --> 00:36:44,070
Dad,

1078
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:45,850
maybe we should go back now.

1079
00:36:46,290 --> 00:36:46,710
Well...

1080
00:36:46,710 --> 00:36:47,770
Disperse! Go back!

1081
00:36:47,800 --> 00:36:48,660
We can't leave!

1082
00:36:48,920 --> 00:36:49,960
We won't leave!

1083
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:52,230
It's all because of you, wretched boy—

1084
00:36:52,230 --> 00:36:54,150
shouting about our family's feng shui site

1085
00:36:54,150 --> 00:36:55,810
until the whole village knew!

1086
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:56,650
I'll teach you a lesson!

1087
00:36:56,650 --> 00:36:58,780
Well, what does this have to do with me?

1088
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:03,360
Everyone, go back, go back!

1089
00:37:03,360 --> 00:37:03,820
Go back!

1090
00:37:04,030 --> 00:37:05,440
Dad, Dad!

1091
00:37:05,710 --> 00:37:06,480
Go! Go home!

1092
00:37:16,960 --> 00:37:17,420
Senior.

1093
00:37:17,500 --> 00:37:18,030
Zhenzhu.

1094
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:20,110
Xiaolan,

1095
00:37:20,110 --> 00:37:21,440
what took you so long?

1096
00:37:21,460 --> 00:37:23,860
You should've seen what happened just now!

1097
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:24,840
I got here a while ago.

1098
00:37:24,840 --> 00:37:26,320
I just went to notify
the subdistrict office.

1099
00:37:26,320 --> 00:37:27,510
Rather than handle it myself,

1100
00:37:27,510 --> 00:37:29,640
it's better to let them take care of it.

1101
00:37:29,800 --> 00:37:31,800
The Luo family will probably
keep coming back.

1102
00:37:31,800 --> 00:37:32,550
With the subdistrict office in charge,

1103
00:37:32,550 --> 00:37:34,280
they won't dare cause trouble.

1104
00:37:34,280 --> 00:37:34,670
Okay.

1105
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:57,320
We can't just let this go.

1106
00:37:58,230 --> 00:37:59,360
I've already given my word to

1107
00:37:59,360 --> 00:38:01,030
the officials
from the Futian Subdistrict Office.

1108
00:38:01,030 --> 00:38:03,070
Please don't go causing trouble again.

1109
00:38:03,070 --> 00:38:03,920
Otherwise, I won't be able to keep

1110
00:38:03,920 --> 00:38:05,440
my position as Chief here!

1111
00:38:06,400 --> 00:38:07,550
You're afraid of losing your post,

1112
00:38:07,550 --> 00:38:08,320
but I'm not!

1113
00:38:15,480 --> 00:38:15,880
Get up!

1114
00:38:16,280 --> 00:38:17,340
Go boil some water!

1115
00:38:18,960 --> 00:38:20,420
How can you just sit there?

1116
00:38:24,510 --> 00:38:26,110
This location is quite nice.

1117
00:38:26,920 --> 00:38:27,510
Xiaolan,

1118
00:38:28,770 --> 00:38:30,420
you hid it really well.

1119
00:38:32,110 --> 00:38:33,000
Mr. Mao,

1120
00:38:33,070 --> 00:38:35,030
I truly wasn't trying to keep it from you.

1121
00:38:35,030 --> 00:38:37,450
It's just that you
attract too much attention.

1122
00:38:37,450 --> 00:38:38,670
I didn't even dare come here often myself—

1123
00:38:38,670 --> 00:38:40,280
afraid someone might swoop in and take it.

1124
00:38:40,280 --> 00:38:41,710
Other developers aside,

1125
00:38:41,960 --> 00:38:43,840
if the Luo family
had caught wind of it early on,

1126
00:38:43,840 --> 00:38:45,800
getting this land
would have been touch-and-go.

1127
00:38:45,800 --> 00:38:47,130
Better safe than sorry.

1128
00:38:51,230 --> 00:38:52,840
The water here is flowing.

1129
00:38:53,320 --> 00:38:55,320
Once you clear away all this debris,

1130
00:38:55,480 --> 00:38:57,760
the condition of the land
will be much clearer.

1131
00:38:57,760 --> 00:38:59,590
The name of this place is awful, though—

1132
00:38:59,590 --> 00:39:00,790
Stinky Bamboo Ditch.

1133
00:39:01,000 --> 00:39:02,630
We have to change it.

1134
00:39:03,070 --> 00:39:03,930
Of course we do.

1135
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:04,590
Stinky Bamboo Ditch

1136
00:39:04,590 --> 00:39:06,400
is just what the local villagers call it.

1137
00:39:06,400 --> 00:39:07,710
I plan to rename it

1138
00:39:07,880 --> 00:39:08,940
Golden Sands Pool.

1139
00:39:09,490 --> 00:39:10,200
Rumor has it

1140
00:39:10,230 --> 00:39:12,230
that gold-bearing sand
springs from the water here.

1141
00:39:12,230 --> 00:39:13,320
Whether that's true or not,

1142
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:14,720
it's an auspicious name.

1143
00:39:15,600 --> 00:39:16,880
There's flowing water
and gold-bearing sand.

1144
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:18,100
Gold mines are rare,

1145
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:19,960
but traces of gold in sand...

1146
00:39:20,440 --> 00:39:21,100
are common.

1147
00:39:22,030 --> 00:39:23,280
I just want to build houses.

1148
00:39:23,280 --> 00:39:25,280
I'm not looking to dig up a gold mine.

1149
00:39:26,030 --> 00:39:27,840
Are gold in the sand and gold mines

1150
00:39:27,840 --> 00:39:29,190
the same thing?

1151
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:30,670
Stop dreaming!

1152
00:39:30,960 --> 00:39:32,800
Sand often contains tiny traces of gold,

1153
00:39:32,800 --> 00:39:34,190
but most of it

1154
00:39:34,190 --> 00:39:35,320
isn't worth mining.

1155
00:39:35,630 --> 00:39:37,320
For that legend to hold true,

1156
00:39:37,760 --> 00:39:40,880
the sand would need to contain
an unusually high amount of gold.

1157
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:41,400
Look.

1158
00:39:41,920 --> 00:39:44,760
These shiny bits are mica fragments,

1159
00:39:44,920 --> 00:39:46,400
not gold in the sand.

1160
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:50,510
In that case,

1161
00:39:50,960 --> 00:39:52,880
we need to tell the legend

1162
00:39:53,590 --> 00:39:54,280
of the gold-bearing sand

1163
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:55,940
as dramatically as possible.

1164
00:39:56,710 --> 00:39:57,360
Ms. Xia,

1165
00:39:57,710 --> 00:39:58,840
I've already sent

1166
00:39:58,840 --> 00:39:59,630
the advertorials about Golden Sands Pool

1167
00:39:59,630 --> 00:40:00,880
and the photos of the Luo family

1168
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:01,510
causing trouble last time

1169
00:40:01,510 --> 00:40:03,280
to various media outlets in Yuesheng.

1170
00:40:03,280 --> 00:40:04,280
But...

1171
00:40:06,030 --> 00:40:06,960
It's okay. Go on.

1172
00:40:07,920 --> 00:40:08,920
Several editors

1173
00:40:08,920 --> 00:40:09,710
knew about the land's

1174
00:40:09,710 --> 00:40:10,840
original condition

1175
00:40:11,190 --> 00:40:12,920
and thought the story
would have no impact.

1176
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:14,380
Some even told me outright

1177
00:40:14,740 --> 00:40:15,880
that the content was too far-fetched

1178
00:40:15,880 --> 00:40:16,510
for serious media outlets

1179
00:40:16,510 --> 00:40:17,910
to run that kind of story.

1180
00:40:18,360 --> 00:40:19,360
Not necessarily.

1181
00:40:19,760 --> 00:40:20,230
Ms. Xia.

1182
00:40:21,150 --> 00:40:21,810
Manager Ge.

1183
00:40:21,840 --> 00:40:22,240
You Li.

1184
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:23,230
I'll be going now.

1185
00:40:23,230 --> 00:40:23,630
Okay.

1186
00:40:24,110 --> 00:40:24,480
Okay.

1187
00:40:32,430 --> 00:40:32,890
Ms. Xia,

1188
00:40:33,480 --> 00:40:34,510
everything you asked for

1189
00:40:34,510 --> 00:40:35,070
is ready.

1190
00:40:36,590 --> 00:40:37,050
Ge Jian,

1191
00:40:37,440 --> 00:40:38,770
come take a look at this.

1192
00:40:48,050 --> 00:40:50,800
Gold-bearing sand
springing from the ground is no legend

1193
00:40:50,800 --> 00:40:53,230
but rather something
we've seen with our own eyes.

1194
00:40:53,230 --> 00:40:56,630
So, this is the gold-bearing sand
springing from the ground.

1195
00:40:57,770 --> 00:40:59,040
[Golden Sands Pool
Construction Project Office]

1196
00:41:14,710 --> 00:41:15,550
Be careful!

1197
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:17,190
Okay!

1198
00:41:24,550 --> 00:41:25,300
What's going on?

1199
00:41:25,300 --> 00:41:25,930
Watch out!

1200
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:26,320
Okay!

1201
00:41:26,360 --> 00:41:26,840
Ms. Xia,

1202
00:41:27,590 --> 00:41:29,790
we've started the silt-clearing work.

1203
00:41:30,840 --> 00:41:32,370
I wonder if this is the sight

1204
00:41:32,470 --> 00:41:33,190
Luo Yaozong's grandfather witnessed

1205
00:41:33,190 --> 00:41:34,190
back in the day.

1206
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:46,570
Boss!

1207
00:41:47,150 --> 00:41:48,750
Looks like we've found gold!

1208
00:41:50,400 --> 00:41:51,000
Boss, look.

1209
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:51,570
There's gold!

1210
00:41:51,570 --> 00:41:52,050
Gold!

1211
00:41:54,890 --> 00:41:55,550
Get back to work.

1212
00:41:55,550 --> 00:41:56,000
Okay.

1213
00:42:08,760 --> 00:42:09,490
Dig! Faster!

1214
00:42:10,610 --> 00:42:11,590
Look, is this it?

1215
00:42:17,110 --> 00:42:17,570
Ms. Xia.

1216
00:42:23,400 --> 00:42:24,150
Stay here and keep an eye on things.

1217
00:42:24,150 --> 00:42:26,210
I'm going to tell my grandpa! Come on!

1218
00:42:34,320 --> 00:42:35,650
Quick, call the police.

1219
00:42:40,070 --> 00:42:41,070
Dig faster! There really is gold!

1220
00:42:41,070 --> 00:42:42,510
There really is!

1221
00:42:51,510 --> 00:42:52,070
Grandpa!

1222
00:42:52,840 --> 00:42:53,370
Grandpa!

1223
00:42:53,800 --> 00:42:55,330
They dug out gold, Grandpa!

1224
00:42:55,510 --> 00:42:56,040
Grandpa!

1225
00:42:57,280 --> 00:42:58,210
They dug up gold!

1226
00:42:58,760 --> 00:42:59,190
That... That...

1227
00:42:59,190 --> 00:43:00,550
That land really yielded gold!

1228
00:43:00,550 --> 00:43:00,960
Quick!

1229
00:43:01,440 --> 00:43:02,030
Get everyone!

1230
00:43:02,030 --> 00:43:02,760
Let's go, let's go!

1231
00:43:02,760 --> 00:43:04,200
Our family's feng shui treasure site—

1232
00:43:04,200 --> 00:43:04,960
we must get it back!

1233
00:43:04,960 --> 00:43:05,800
Let's go! Go!
